# ── Captured Artifactory state — DO NOT COMMIT in this public repo ─────────
# `mode: backup` writes <env>/artifactory.{yml,json} here, plus sidecars
# (system-config XML, .drift.yml, .merged.yml). A capture contains real internal
# detail — instance hostname, LDAP manager/group DNs, user emails, the full
# system-config descriptor. This repository is public, so captures are ignored;
# only this .gitignore and README.md are tracked, to keep the structure
# documented. For a git-tracked As-Built history, point artifactory_state_dir at
# a PRIVATE location instead.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
